ì·¨í–¥:
- ê¸°ë¶„: ${moods.find(m => m.id === preferences.mood)?.label || 'ë¯¸ì„ íƒ'}
- ì¥ë¥´: ${preferences.genres.join(', ') || 'ë¯¸ì„ íƒ'}
- ì¢‹ì•„í•œ ì˜í™”: ${movieRef || 'ë¯¸ì…ë ¥'}
${myReviews.length > 0 ? `- ë†’ì€ í‰ì : ${myReviews.filter(r => r.rating >= 4).map(r => r.title).slice(0, 5).join(', ')}` : ''}

3í¸ ì¶”ì²œ. JSONë§Œ: [{"title": "ì œëª©", "year": 2020, "genres": ["ì¥ë¥´"], "reason": "ì´ìœ  2ë¬¸ì¥"}]`;

